---
description: Apply the repository Symfony conventions when working in a Symfony codebase.
globs:
  - "**/*.php"
  - "config/**/*.yaml"
  - "config/**/*.yml"
  - "templates/**/*.twig"
  - "composer.json"
---

When this rule matches, read and follow `.github/instructions/symfony.instructions.md`.

Use that file as the canonical source for Symfony layering, framework integrations, and configuration expectations.